e blessings of Allah is the best act of worship.\u201d Source: Tafsi\u0304r Ibn Kathi\u0304r 3:190 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0643\u062b\u064a\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u0632\u0650 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24428,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/02\/14\/tafakkur-blessings-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33277,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tafakkur: Reflect deeply on the blessings of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 14, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cReflect deeply upon the blessings of Allah, but do not reflect upon the essence of Allah.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 6319 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27034,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/01\/15\/hasid-enemy-qadr-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33277,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Hasad: Envier is an enemy to the decree of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Qurtubi reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cDo not be an enemy to the blessings of Allah.\u201d It was said, \u201cWho is an enemy to the blessings of Allah?\u201d Ibn Mas\u2019ud said, \u201cThose who envy people for what Allah has given them of his favor.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14890,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/do-not-neglect-suhur\/","url_meta":{"origin":33277,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Suhoor: Do not neglect blessed pre-fasting meal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Harith reported: A man among the companions entered upon the Prophet while he was eating the pre-fasting meal. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, it is a blessing that Allah has given you, so do not abandon it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2162 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29335,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/13\/let-allah-see-traces-blessings\/","url_meta":{"origin":33277,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Let Allah see the traces of His blessings on you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik ibn Nadlah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf Allah has given you wealth, let the traces of his blessings and generosity be seen upon you.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4063 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0645\u0627\u0644\u0643 \u0628\u0646 \u0646\u0636\u0644\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0634\u0645\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33277","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=33277"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33277\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=33277"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abu